  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a6db61ac296f850429f2dc6daef8dd23, type: 3}
  m_Name: Annes Letter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  LetterText: "I\u2019ve admired you for a long time, but now I want to make you
    mine. There is a gala tonight that we\u2019ll both be attending. You\u2019ll
    have to find me in the crowd, I like playing hard to get\u2026 Ask the notable
    guest at the party, I\u2019ll be one of them. Here some stuff to look out for:\r\n\r\nI
    hope you have good moves on the dance floor, though I doubt you\u2019ll outperform
    me! Find someone who\u2019s a great dancer, it might be yours truly\u2026\r\n\r\nOne
    thing about me is that I\u2019m not afraid of a little flirting! If you ask me
    out, I won\u2019t get embarrassed. Your secret lover is someone who\u2019s NOT
    shy about romance\u2026\r\n\r\nThe early worm get got! You\u2019ll not see me
    at sunup, but always at sun down. The person you\u2019re looking for is a nightowl,
    through and though\u2026\r\n\r\nI envy the bird sometimes, high and free in the
    sky\u2026 That means I\u2019m not afraid of heights! To find me, you\u2019ll
    have to find someone who doesn\u2019t fear high altitude!\r\n\r\nLooking at the
    guest list, I think most of these people don\u2019t know anything about good
    booze! Find someone who has an expensive taste when it comes to alcohol\u2026\r\n\r\nI
    promise I\u2019ll be the only one who matches this exact description, but talk
    to as many people as possible. Some people may have one or more matching interests\u2026"
  rightAnswer: 5
  hintKills: 060000000100000004000000
